function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	idAsaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_Kehj_Armor_01_AsaFollower")
		
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAsaFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idAsaFollower)

		Hydra.QActorWait(idAsaFollower, 0.5)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(idAsaFollower, actor_AsaBossOver, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_WALK, true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idAsaFollower, idActorKilled)

		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actor_AsaBossOver, idAsaFollower)

		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idAsaFollower,"NPC_Idle_Stand_Ponder")
		
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idAsaFollower)
	end
